{"id":60403,"date":"2023-04-26T08:30:12","date_gmt":"2023-04-26T13:30:12","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/?p=60403"},"modified":"2024-05-17T14:43:21","modified_gmt":"2024-05-17T19:43:21","slug":"16-simple-meaningful-mothers-day-marketing-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2022\/04\/25\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas","title":{"rendered":"16 Simple, Meaningful Mother&#8217;s Day Marketing Ideas"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Confession: I feel a little guilty writing this post. Why? Because the original creator of Mother&#8217;s Day, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bbc.com\/news\/stories-52589173\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Anna Jarvis<\/a>, became disgusted with the holiday for its becoming so commercialized\u2014yes even back in 1920\u2014that she dedicated much of her life legally campaigning against the holiday.<\/p>\n<p>And here I am, writing a post about Mother&#8217;s Day <em>marketing<\/em> ideas. But I think AJ (Yes? No? Only close friends and fam?) will approve of these, since they&#8217;re less about selling and more about connecting with your audience\u2014and not just mothers\u2014in meaningful ways.<\/p>\n<p>So maybe you could give it a read and let me know what you think?<\/p>\n<h2>Mother&#8217;s Day marketing ideas<\/h2>\n<p>Okay AJ, here goes nothin&#8217;.<\/p>\n<h3>1. Prioritize inclusivity<\/h3>\n<p>First and foremost, remember that Mother&#8217;s Day isn&#8217;t a happy day for everyone. It can be a struggle for women who have lost a child, for mothers who have lost a mother, for children who don&#8217;t have a mother. Consider providing your audience with an opt-out for Mother&#8217;s Day material or adjusting your messaging to recognize these groups.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-inclusive-opt-out.png\" alt=\"mothers day marketing ideas - inclusive opt out messaging\" width=\"720\" height=\"536\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60417\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-inclusive-opt-out.png 720w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-inclusive-opt-out-480x357.png 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 720px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.independent.co.uk\/life-style\/women\/mothers-day-emails-opt-out-b2043940.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Image source<\/em><\/a><\/p>\n<p>\ud83d\udc97 Get inclusive marketing ideas for Mother&#8217;s Day and beyond. <strong>Free guide &gt;&gt;<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/marketing.localiq.com\/WSLIQContentDLWebsite2024MarketingCalendar.html?cid=Web_WS_InContent_Guide_2024MarketingCalendar_Download\">The Mega Must-Have Marketing Calendar<\/a><\/p>\n<h3>2. Support a nonprofit organization<\/h3>\n<p>Another option in the name of compassion and inclusivity would be to donate a portion of your proceeds to a nonprofit such as for pregnancy loss or orphans. This will raise awareness while also helping your customers feel good about their Mother\u2019s Day purchases.<\/p>\n<p>Here are some lists of nonprofits dedicated to:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.verywellfamily.com\/miscarriage-support-organizations-2371339\">Pregnancy loss<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.verywellfamily.com\/leading-infant-and-maternal-health-charities-and-organizations-4146549\">Maternal and infant health<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/impactful.ninja\/best-charities-for-helping-orphans\/\">Orphans<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-infant-loss-nonprofit.png\" alt=\"mothers day marketing ideas - nonprofit for pregnancy loss\" width=\"600\" height=\"217\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60410\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-infant-loss-nonprofit.png 600w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-infant-loss-nonprofit-480x174.png 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 600px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.threelittlebirdsperinatal.org\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Image source<\/em><\/a><\/p>\n<h3>3. Promote a sustainable Mother\u2019s Day<\/h3>\n<p>Here&#8217;s yet another unique way to commemorate this holiday. Mother Earth, Mother Nature, however you refer to her\u2014she needs some love too! You might:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Encourage your customers to save paper by sending ecards or, as was Anna Jarvis&#8217;s vision, wear a single white carnation badge.<\/li>\n<li>Find neighborhood cleanups they can volunteer at with their mothers.<\/li>\n<li>Plant a tree for every nth purchase.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-sustainability.png\" alt=\"mothers day marketing ideas - sustainability\" width=\"720\" height=\"423\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60411\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-sustainability.png 720w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-sustainability-480x282.png 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 720px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/99designs.com\/blog\/business\/eco-friendly-brands\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Image source<\/em><\/a><\/p>\n<h3>4. Create a Mother\u2019s Day gift guide<\/h3>\n<p>Okay so Anna probably wouldn&#8217;t like this one that much, but the reality is, people buy gifts for mothers on Mother&#8217;s Day and that&#8217;s not going to change. And they don&#8217;t want to give a single carnation. They want to be unique. Creative. Personal.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-gift-guide-search.png\" alt=\"mothers day marketing ideas - gift ideas google search\" width=\"600\" height=\"579\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60405\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-gift-guide-search.png 600w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-gift-guide-search-480x463.png 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 600px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p>So why not compile a Mother&#8217;s Day gift guide for those in your audience. It doesn&#8217;t have to be of products or services you offer. In fact, if you don&#8217;t offer anything relevant, it can consist entirely of others&#8217; products\/services. Content marketing is about adding value for your audience, sometimes purely altruistically.<\/p>\n<p>You can also use this guide as a way to send referral business to fellow local businesses, partners, or potential new partners.<\/p>\n<p>Use these <a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/mothers-day-slogans\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Mother&#8217;s Day slogans<\/a> to promote your gift guide.<\/p>\n<h3>5. Publish an interactive piece of content<\/h3>\n<p>Instead of a regular static gift guide, use a tool like <a href=\"https:\/\/outgrow.co\">Outgrow<\/a> to build <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2020\/08\/04\/interactive-content\">interactive content<\/a> like the quiz below. You can even incorporate gift recommendations based on the type of mom they have.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-mom-quiz-gift.png\" alt=\"mothers day marketing ideas - quiz \" width=\"720\" height=\"450\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60409\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-mom-quiz-gift.png 720w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-mom-quiz-gift-480x300.png 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 720px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.1800flowers.com\/blog\/celebrate-occasions\/showcasing-parents\/moms\/unique-gift-ideas-for-non-traditional-moms\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Image source<\/em><\/a><\/p>\n<p>\ud83d\udea8 Get copy-and-paste social media posts ready to go for April (and every month of 2024) in our <a href=\"https:\/\/marketing.localiq.com\/WSLIQContentDLWebsiteMonthlySocialMediaCalendarTemplate.html?cid=Web_WS_InContent_Template_MonthlySocialMediaCalendar_Download\">free social media template<\/a>!<\/p>\n<h3>6. Invite personal sharing<\/h3>\n<p>As a way to avoid the generic, commercialized nature of Mother\u2019s Day marketing, simply start a conversation on Facebook. Share your personal reflections, experiences, or memories, and ask your followers to share theirs. Include the happy, the sad, and everything in between.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/social-media-marketing\">Social media marketing<\/a> is a two-way street. Your followers want to feel heard and they&#8217;ll also appreciate your transparency.<\/p>\n<h3>7. Host a simple event<\/h3>\n<p>There are a number of free and easy events you can put on for your customers on or before Mother&#8217;s Day with attractions like:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Free treats and refreshments, music, and a raffle.<\/li>\n<li>A DIY photo booth or other <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2020\/02\/13\/ugc-instagram\">user-generated-content<\/a>-friendly opportunities to spread brand awareness.<\/li>\n<li>A \u201cgrab bag\u201d for moms or free gift to the first people who arrive at the party.<\/li>\n<li>Mother&#8217;s Day gift making.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-craft-making.jpeg\" alt=\"mothers day marketing ideas - gift making event\" width=\"600\" height=\"363\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60416\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-craft-making.jpeg 600w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-craft-making-480x290.jpeg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 600px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/hunterliggett.armymwr.com\/view-event\/mothers-day-craft-making\/5116086\/58598\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Image source<\/em><\/a><\/p>\n<h3>8. Offer a discount<\/h3>\n<p>Mother\u2019s Day is an important gift-giving holiday, so what better way to attract customers than by offering a Mother\u2019s Day discount or<a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2020\/10\/13\/sales-promotion-examples\"> promotion<\/a>? A few ways to do that could be to:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Display a discount wheel that can be spun upon entering the store<\/li>\n<li>An exclusive offer for bringing in a childhood photo with mom<\/li>\n<li>A <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/best-time-to-post-on-social-media\">post on social media<\/a> that gives a discount only to those who follow your social pages.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>9. Run a Mother\u2019s Day giveaway<\/h3>\n<p>Run an <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2017\/05\/11\/instagram-giveaways\">Instagram giveaway<\/a> before Mother&#8217;s Day for a chance to win a gift for mom (or yourself, if you are a mom). To help you <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/get-more-instagram-followers\">get more followers<\/a> and expand your reach, contestants can enter by using a branded <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2019\/05\/29\/instagram-hashtags\">hashtag<\/a> and\/or tagging a friend.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-giveaway.png\" alt=\"mothers day marketing ideas - giveaway\" width=\"600\" height=\"366\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60406\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-giveaway.png 600w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-giveaway-480x293.png 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 600px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p>For (lots) more, LocaliQ has you covered with these <a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/happy-mothers-day-social-media-post-ideas\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Mother&#8217;s Day social media post ideas, tips, and templates<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h3>10. Publish a \u201cthings to do on Mother\u2019s Day\u201d list<\/h3>\n<p>Similar to creating a gift guide, get some <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2020\/12\/15\/local-marketing-ideas\">local marketing<\/a> into the mix by writing an email or blog post about things to do in your area on Mother&#8217;s Day. Once again, this is a good opportunity to build trust with your audience and also potential partnerships with the businesses you refer them to. This is a great option use throughout your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/may-content-ideas\">May content<\/a> calendar.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-things-to-do.png\" alt=\"mothers day marketing ideas - things to do list\" width=\"600\" height=\"498\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60418\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-things-to-do.png 600w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-things-to-do-480x398.png 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 600px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.uber.com\/newsroom\/11-popular-mothers-day-activities-in-boston\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Image source<\/em><\/a><\/p>\n<h3>11. Do a multi-cultural Instagram Story takeover<\/h3>\n<p>Here&#8217;s a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2022\/03\/01\/instagram-story-ideas\">creative Instagram Story idea<\/a>: share your Instagram creds with a handful of mothers on your team and give them each a day or hour of the day to cover. They can share a day in the life of a mother for their family type, culture, and lifestyle. This is an easy way to celebrate diversity and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2015\/12\/23\/humanize-brand\">humanize your brand<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h3>12. Send a care package<\/h3>\n<p>If you have a small client base, consider sending a personal greeting card or gift to your mom clients. It can be something simple, like a candle, a succulent, flowers, or a growable planter gift. Simply letting them know you\u2019re thinking of them can go a long way in<a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2021\/06\/21\/build-client-relationships\"> establishing strong client relationships<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-plant-gift.png\" alt=\"mothers day marketing ideas - planter gift\" width=\"600\" height=\"599\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60412\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-plant-gift.png 600w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-plant-gift-480x479.png 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 600px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.baudville.com\/products\/growable-praise-plant-kit-lucky?utm_source=Froogle_UnBrand&amp;utm_medium=cse&amp;utm_term=&amp;utm_campaign=Shopping+-+Plant+Cubes+-+UnBrand&amp;utm_source=adwords&amp;utm_medium=ppc&amp;hsa_acc=1188619435&amp;hsa_cam=10596554285&amp;hsa_grp=104784407997&amp;hsa_ad=450094565011&amp;hsa_src=u&amp;hsa_tgt=pla-1647055916570&amp;hsa_kw=&amp;hsa_mt=&amp;hsa_net=adwords&amp;hsa_ver=3&amp;gclid=CjwKCAjwx46TBhBhEiwArA_DjN2Jjmq9EKf_gkP_ekLihzAMOJjstnqc1PxIKcBZaHd-8nDwZKxA_xoCjV4QAvD_BwE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Image source<\/em><\/a><\/p>\n<h3>13. Use creative imagery<\/h3>\n<p>Instead of the traditional floral, heart, and pink imagery we see everywhere in Mother&#8217;s Day <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2022\/04\/04\/marketing-collateral\">marketing collateral<\/a>, go for something more creative or abstract. Take a page out of Coca Cola&#8217;s book, for example:<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-coke-ads.png\" alt=\"mothers day marketing ideas - coke ads\" width=\"600\" height=\"668\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60413\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-coke-ads.png 600w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-coke-ads-480x534.png 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 600px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/CocaColaAfrica\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Image source<\/em><\/a><\/p>\n<h3>14. Use templates<\/h3>\n<p>Whether you&#8217;re looking for <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2022\/03\/10\/facebook-post-ideas\">Facebook post ideas<\/a>, an Instagram Story to create, a physical postcard, or website graphic, Canva has a number of Mother\u2019s Day templates that can save you time and polish off your look.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-instagram-story-templates.png\" alt=\"mothers day marketing ideas - canva templates\" width=\"720\" height=\"406\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60408\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-instagram-story-templates.png 720w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-instagram-story-templates-480x271.png 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 720px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canva.com\/templates\/?query=mothers-day-instagram-stories\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Image source<\/em><\/a><\/p>\n<p>And for the uninitiated, here&#8217;s <a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/how-to-use-canva\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">our tutorial on how to use Canva<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h3>15. Send out a Mother\u2019s Day email<\/h3>\n<p>There are a few different approaches you can take with your Mother&#8217;s Day email.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Send out a personalized happy Mother\u2019s Day email to your clients (but keep it inclusive).<\/li>\n<li>Send out a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/mothers-day-messages\">marketing email<\/a> with Mother&#8217;s Day discounts and promotions you&#8217;re running.<\/li>\n<li>Compile a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2021\/02\/25\/email-newsletter-ideas\">newsletter<\/a> with a mix of announcements, resources, and tips. Include your gift guide, things to do list, and giveaway instructions, of course.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-email.png\" alt=\"mothers day marketing ideas - email example\" width=\"510\" height=\"1122\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60414\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-email.png 510w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-email-480x1056.png 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 510px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><a href=\"https:\/\/reallygoodemails.com\/emails\/happy-mothers-day-from-nanit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Image source<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n<h3>16. Have a countdown<\/h3>\n<p>Anna wouldn&#8217;t approve of this one either, I don&#8217;t think. But <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2017\/04\/05\/how-to-increase-urgency\">urgency<\/a> in marketing is key. Create a countdown for your customers so they know when your promotion or offer expires. Or simply remind them of how much time they have in your social posts.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-countdown-twitter.jpg\" alt=\"mothers day marketing ideas - twitter post with countdown\" width=\"500\" height=\"664\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60415\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-countdown-twitter.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/mothers-day-marketing-ideas-countdown-twitter-480x637.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 500px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<h2>Mother&#8217;s Day marketing ideas recap<\/h2>\n<p>No, Mother&#8217;s Day will never be the simple single-white-carnation-wearing day Anna wanted it to be, but there are plenty of simple ways your business can recognize the holiday in such a manner that prioritizes virtues over sales. And those simple Mother&#8217;s Day marketing ideas include:<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>Be inclusive<\/li>\n<li>Support a nonprofit organization<\/li>\n<li>Sustainable Mother\u2019s Day<\/li>\n<li>Create a Mother\u2019s Day gift guide<\/li>\n<li>Create interactive content<\/li>\n<li>Invite personal sharing<\/li>\n<li>Host a simple event<\/li>\n<li>Offer a discount<\/li>\n<li>Run a Mother\u2019s Day giveaway<\/li>\n<li>Publish a \u201cthings to do on Mother\u2019s Day\u201d list<\/li>\n<li>Do a multicultural Instagram Story takeover<\/li>\n<li>Send a care package<\/li>\n<li>Use creative imagery<\/li>\n<li>Use templates<\/li>\n<li>Send out a Mother\u2019s Day email<\/li>\n<li>Have a countdown<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Plus find out why the creator of Mother&#8217;s Day was determined to cancel it.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":87,"featured_media":60492,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"_et_pb_use_builder":"","_et_pb_old_content":"","_et_gb_content_width":"","om_disable_all_campaigns":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[96],"tags":[],"dipi_cpt_category":[],"class_list":["post-60403","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-seasonal-marketing"],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v25.8 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>16 Simple, Meaningful Mother&#039;s Day Marketing Ideas | WordStream<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Connect with your audience this May with these simple, affordable Mother&#039;s Day Marketing ideas for your blog, social, email, events, and more.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2022\/04\/25\/mothers-d